title: Sony PSP custom firmware 6.60 jailbreak
description:
Copy the contents from this package to the root root of your PSP . Then start your PSP and run PROUPDATE from your XMB. The CIPL_Flasher allows you to make this jailbreak firmware permanent on your system.
Remember that your battery should be charged OR the PSP should be cord-powered.

DO KEEP IN MIND that this jailbreak firmware should only be used to run home-brew programs and to backup your UMDs so you can play them from the PSP's memory stick or on your PC through an emulator.
I AM NOT PROVIDING THIS TO BE USED TO PLAY PIRATED GAMES!
